QuestData.Title: Free Freewind Post
QuestData.Description: Alas, it's time for you to leave. How quickly the chicks fall from the nest. Or, something.$B$BAnyway, you've done solid work here, my friend, but Quentin and the night elves have been crying that they urgently need your help with the Grimtotem at Freewind Post to the northwest.$B$BIf you ask me, it's a lost cause, but who knows... maybe with your help they'll actually succeed?
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Quentin at Freewind Post in Thousand Needles.
QuestData.RewardText: I'm glad that Fizzle finally sent you here. We're helping the tauren to retake Freewind Post and push back the Grimtotem.
